OL,3,CMartyn's Law overcomes final hurdle in
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,FA proposed law that aims to prevent
OL,7,Fand reduce the harm of terror attacks
OL,8,Fat event venues has moved a step
OL,9,Fcloser to becoming law.
OL,11,FMartyn's Law was first proposed by
OL,12,FFigen Murray after she lost her son
OL,13,FMartyn Hett in the Manchester Arena
OL,14,Fbombing in May 2017.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday 25 March, MPs voted in
OL,17,Ffavour of amendments made by the House
OL,18,Fof Lords, meaning Martins Law will now
OL,19,Fbe sent for sent for royal assent.
