OL,3,CMartyn's Law overcomes final hurdle in
OL,4,CParliament
OL,6,F"To have lost her son, Martyn Hett in
OL,7,Fthe Manchester Arena attack in May of
OL,8,F2017, and to have yet still found the
OL,9,Fstrength to drive this campaign
OL,10,Fforward is both inspiring and
OL,11,Fphenomenal.
OL,13,F"And I know that all members right
OL,14,Facross this House will join me in
OL,15,Fpaying tribute to Figen. Figen had
OL,16,Fpreviously said, it's time to get this
OL,17,Fdone, and I am very proud to say that
OL,18,Fthis Government has done just that."
